coffee.Title: Vanilla Latte
coffee.Discription: Indulge in the rich, creamy taste of our Vanilla Latte, a classic coffeehouse favorite. This delightful beverage combines the smooth, robust flavor of freshly brewed espresso with the velvety texture of steamed milk. Infused with the sweet and aromatic essence of premium vanilla syrup, each sip offers a perfect balance of coffee and sweetness. Our Vanilla Latte is a harmonious blend of bold espresso and creamy milk, complemented by the sweet, fragrant notes of vanilla. The espresso provides a rich, full-bodied base, while the steamed milk adds a silky smoothness that enhances the overall drinking experience. The vanilla syrup adds a touch of sweetness and a delightful aroma, making this beverage a comforting and satisfying choice.
coffee.Ingredients: Freshly brewed espresso, Steamed milk, Vanilla syrup, Topped with a light froth

coffee.Discription: Indulge in the pure essence of coffee with our expertly crafted Espresso. coffee.Discription: Indulge in our classic Grilled Cheese Sandwich, a perfect blend of gooey, melted cheese and crispy, golden-brown bread. Whether you’re pairing it with a hot cup of coffee or enjoying it on its own, our Grilled Cheese Sandwich is sure to satisfy your cravings.

coffee.Title: Coffee Ice cream
coffee.Discription: Indulge in the rich and creamy delight of our Coffee Ice Cream, crafted to perfection for coffee lovers. This luxurious treat combines the robust flavor of freshly brewed coffee with the smooth texture of premium ice cream, offering a delightful escape with every scoop. Perfect for a refreshing dessert on a warm day or a delightful treat anytime, our Coffee Ice Cream is sure to satisfy your sweet tooth and caffeine cravings all at once.
coffee.Ingredients: Freshly Brewed Coffee, Heavy Cream, Whole Milk, Egg Yolks, Sugar, Vanilla Extract

coffee.Title: Frozen Waffles
coffee.Discription: Our frozen waffles are a perfect blend of crispy on the outside and fluffy on the inside, offering a delightful breakfast or snack option. Made with high-quality ingredients, these waffles are quick and easy to prepare, providing a delicious and convenient treat that can be enjoyed with your favorite toppings, such as fresh fruits, syrup, or a dollop of whipped cream.
coffee.Ingredients: Flour, sugar, eggs, milk, butter, baking powder, salt, vanilla extract

coffee.Title: Chocolate Waffles
coffee.Discription: Indulge in our decadent chocolate waffles, a perfect blend of rich cocoa and fluffy batter. Each waffle is expertly crafted to offer a crispy exterior with a soft, melt-in-your-mouth interior. Ideal for breakfast or a delightful dessert, these waffles are sure to satisfy your chocolate cravings.
coffee.Ingredients: All-purpose flour, cocoa powder, sugar, baking powder, salt, eggs, milk, butter, vanilla extract, chocolate chips.

coffee.Title: Oat milk latte
coffee.Discription: Experience the rich and creamy delight of our Oat Milk Latte, a perfect blend of smooth espresso and velvety oat milk. This dairy-free alternative offers a subtly sweet and nutty flavor, providing a comforting and satisfying beverage that's gentle on the stomach and environmentally friendly. Ideal for those seeking a plant-based option without compromising on taste and texture.
coffee.Ingredients: Espresso, Oat Milk, Water, Natural Flavors

coffee.Title: Iced shaken espresso
coffee.Discription: Our Iced Shaken Espresso is a refreshing and invigorating blend, perfect for a hot day. It features rich espresso, expertly shaken to create a frothy, chilled drink that highlights the robust coffee flavors. Lightly sweetened and served over ice, it's a delightful treat for any coffee lover.
coffee.Ingredients: Espresso shots, ice, simple syrup, water, milk (optional), flavored syrups (optional, e.g., vanilla, caramel, hazelnut)

coffee.Title: cappuccino Coffee
coffee.Discription: A cappuccino is a classic coffee drink that blends equal parts of espresso, steamed milk, and frothed milk. This delightful beverage is known for its rich and robust flavor, complemented by the creamy texture of the milk. Perfect for a morning boost or an afternoon treat, a cappuccino offers a harmonious balance of strong coffee and smooth milk, often topped with a light dusting of cocoa powder or cinnamon for an added touch of indulgence.
coffee.Ingredients: Espresso, Steamed Milk, Frothed Milk, Cocoa Powder (optional), Cinnamon (optional)

coffee.Title: Iced Mocha Cookie Crumble Latte
coffee.Discription: Indulge in the rich and creamy Iced Mocha Cookie Crumble Latte, a delightful blend of smooth espresso, velvety chocolate, and crunchy cookie crumbles. Topped with a swirl of whipped cream and a sprinkle of chocolate cookie crumbles, this refreshing treat is perfect for satisfying your sweet tooth and coffee cravings.
coffee.Ingredients: Espresso, milk, chocolate syrup, cookie crumbles, whipped cream, ice

coffee.Title: Stardust Macchiato
coffee.Discription: The Stardust Macchiato is a celestial blend of rich espresso and creamy steamed milk, topped with a delicate drizzle of caramel and a sprinkle of edible glitter. Perfectly balanced and irresistibly smooth, this enchanting beverage will transport you to a galaxy of flavor with every sip

Perfect for a light lunch or a tasty snack, this sandwich offers a burst of Mediterranean flavors in every bite.
coffee.Ingredients: Artisan bread, fresh basil leaves, ripe tomatoes, mozzarella cheese, balsamic glaze, olive oil, salt, pepper

coffee.Title: Bake In Pesto Veggie Sourdough Sandwich

This sandwich features a hearty combination of fresh, roasted vegetables and creamy pesto, all nestled between slices of our artisan sourdough bread. Perfectly grilled to a golden crisp, it’s a delightful vegetarian option that satisfies your cravings and nourishes your soul.

coffee.Title: Mushroom Cheese Melt Baguette Sandwich
coffee.Discription: The Mushroom Cheese Melt Baguette Sandwich is a delightful combination of savory mushrooms, creamy melted cheese, and fresh baguette bread. Perfectly toasted to golden brown, this sandwich offers a satisfying crunch with every bite, complemented by the rich and earthy flavors of the mushrooms and the gooey, melted cheese. coffee.Title: Brussels Waffle
coffee.Discription: Brussels Waffles are a classic Belgian treat known for their light, airy texture and crisp exterior. These waffles are typically rectangular, with deep pockets perfect for holding syrup, whipped cream, or fresh fruit. They are traditionally enjoyed as a breakfast or dessert item, offering a delightful combination of sweetness and crunch.
coffee.Ingredients: flour, sugar, baking powder, salt, eggs, milk, melted butter, vanilla extract, yeast

coffee.Title: Belgium Waffle
coffee.Discription: Indulge in our classic Belgium Waffle, a delightful treat that's crispy on the outside and fluffy on the inside. Perfectly golden and served with a dusting of powdered sugar, it's an ideal breakfast or dessert option. Enjoy it with a drizzle of maple syrup, a dollop of whipped cream, and fresh berries for a burst of flavor in every bite.
coffee.Ingredients: Flour, sugar, baking powder, salt, milk, eggs, butter, vanilla extract

coffee.Ingredients: Flour, sugar, baking powder, salt, milk, eggs, butter, vanilla extract

coffee.Title: Toaster Waffle
coffee.Discription: Our Toaster Waffle is a delightful breakfast treat that combines the classic crispy texture with a rich, buttery flavor. Perfectly golden and ready to pop in the toaster, these waffles are an easy and delicious way to start your day.

coffee.Discription: Savor the irresistible crunch and soft, chewy interior of our Hong Kong Egg Waffles. A beloved street snack transformed into a delightful treat at our coffee shop. Each waffle is meticulously crafted to perfection, ensuring a nostalgic taste of Hong Kong's bustling streets with every bite.

coffee.Title: Waffle Cone

coffee.Ingredients: Flour, sugar, eggs, butter, vanilla extract, salt

coffee.Title: Pizzelle

coffee.Title: Stroopwafel

coffee.Title: Seafood Sandwich
coffee.Discription: Dive into the ocean of flavor with our Seafood Sandwich. Packed with fresh seafood goodness, this sandwich is a savory delight that will transport your taste buds seaside.
coffee.Ingredients: Freshly baked artisan bread, shrimp, crab meat, mayonnaise, celery, lemon juice, salt, pepper.

coffee.Title: Roast Beef Sandwich
coffee.Discription: Enjoy our savory Roast Beef Sandwich, crafted to satisfy your cravings with every bite. Tender slices of seasoned roast beef nestled between soft, freshly baked bread, complemented by a medley of crisp vegetables and a hint of tangy sauce.

coffee.Title: Ham Sandwich
coffee.Discription: Savor the classic combination of savory ham nestled between slices of fresh, crusty bread. Our Ham Sandwich is a delightful blend of simplicity and taste, perfect for any time of day.
coffee.Ingredients: Ham, bread (such as ciabatta or whole wheat), lettuce, tomato, mayonnaise, mustard

coffee.Title: Nutella Sandwich
coffee.Discription: Indulge in a delightful blend of creamy Nutella spread between two slices of freshly toasted bread, creating the perfect balance of sweetness and satisfaction.
coffee.Ingredients: Nutella spread, bread (white or whole wheat), butter.

coffee.Title: Grilled Chicken Sandwich
coffee.Discription: Savor the delicious blend of tender grilled chicken, fresh vegetables, and zesty sauces nestled between two slices of artisanal whole-grain bread. Our Grilled Chicken Sandwich is a wholesome choice that satisfies with every bite.

Blog.Title: From Bean to Brew
Blog.Content:
Have you ever wondered about the journey your morning coffee takes before it reaches your cup? At Coffee street, we believe that understanding this journey enhances your appreciation for every sip. Let's take a peek behind the scenes—from bean to brew.

1. Sourcing the Finest Beans:
It all begins with the selection of high-quality coffee beans. We work closely with coffee farmers from renowned regions across the globe, ensuring that every bean meets our rigorous standards for taste, aroma, and sustainability. This commitment not only guarantees exceptional flavor but also supports ethical farming practices.

2. Expert Roasting Process:
Once the beans arrive at our roastery, our expert roasters take over. Roasting is a delicate art that transforms raw green beans into the aromatic wonders we love. Each batch is carefully roasted to bring out unique flavors and profiles, whether it's a rich dark roast or a smooth medium blend. Our roasters blend science with passion to ensure consistency and quality in every batch.

3. Precision Grinding for Freshness:
To preserve the beans' freshness and flavor, we grind them just before packaging. Grinding coffee exposes more surface area to oxygen, which can quickly degrade its quality. By grinding on demand, we ensure that every cup maintains the fullness of its flavor profile, whether it's brewed in a drip machine or a French press.

4. Delivering Perfection to Your Doorstep:
Finally, your perfect cup of coffee is packaged with care and delivered directly to your doorstep. Our commitment to quality extends beyond the roast—it's about delivering an experience that elevates your mornings. Whether you prefer single-origin beans, flavored blends, or delectable espresso options, our diverse selection ensures there's something to suit every palate.
